                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>
                            <emphasis>GUI model</emphasis>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry rowsep="1">
                        <para>The graphical presentation of a <trademark>jACOB</trademark>
                            application is charcterized by its GUI model. The GUI model ifself is based on
                            the data model of the application design of
                            the <trademark>jACOB</trademark> application.</para>
                        <para>The GUI model is composed of:</para>
                        <itemizedlist>
                            <listitem>
                                <para>forms,</para>
                            </listitem>
                            <listitem>
                                <para>
                                    <glossterm linkend="domain">domains</glossterm> and</para>
                            </listitem>
                            <listitem>
                                <para>
                                    <glossterm linkend="GUIHooks">GUI hooks</glossterm>.</para>
                            </listitem>
                        </itemizedlist>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>
                            <emphasis>Creation of a GUI model</emphasis>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry rowsep="1">
                        <para>The creation of such a GUI model will be explained in the following sections:</para>
